summary: The document is a declassified record associated with the President John F. Kennedy Assassination Records Act of 1992, detailing information about individuals from Cuba who arrived in Madrid in December 1979. It provides personal details such as names, dates of birth, and places of birth, alongside references to file numbers and its classification as secret.
key_findings: Document is part of the 2025 release under the President John F. Kennedy Assassination Records Act of 1992.
Contains information on individuals from Cuba arriving in Madrid on 12 December 1979.
Includes personal details such as names, dates of birth, and places of birth for the individuals mentioned.
Mentions file numbers and indicates the document's classification as secret.
